# 金融行业新一代数据仓库解决方案

## 下载

### Docker

```
docker pull apachecn0/jinrong-xingye-xinyidai-shujucangku-jiejuefangan
docker run -tid -p <port>:80 apachecn0/jinrong-xingye-xinyidai-shujucangku-jiejuefangan
# 访问 http://localhost:{port} 查看文档
```

### PYPI

```
pip install jinrong-xingye-xinyidai-shujucangku-jiejuefangan
jinrong-xingye-xinyidai-shujucangku-jiejuefangan <port>
# 访问 http://localhost:{port} 查看文档
```

### NPM

```
npm install -g jinrong-xingye-xinyidai-shujucangku-jiejuefangan
jinrong-xingye-xinyidai-shujucangku-jiejuefangan <port>
# 访问 http://localhost:{port} 查看文档
```
